required_parameters.description: The value of dest_type field returned in …/auto-complete.

required_parameters.description: The value of  lable field returned in …/auto-complete.
required_parameters.default: New York, New York State, United States

required_parameters.description: The value of dest_id field returned in …/auto-complete.

optional_parameters.name: other_filters
optional_parameters.description:
filters -> options -> urlId in …/stays/list.
You can select more than one, separated by commas. Ex:ht_id=204,di=929,ht_id=201

optional_parameters.name: popular_activities
optional_parameters.description:
Beach<->Hot_tub_Jacuzzi<->Golf_course<->Fishing<->Hiking.Bicycle_rental<->Fitness
You can select more than one, separated by commas.

optional_parameters.name: property_accessibility
optional_parameters.description:
- Wheelchair_accessible
- Visual_aids_Braille
- Visual_aids_tactile_signs
- Auditory_guidance
You can select more than one, separated by commas.

optional_parameters.name: distance_from_center
optional_parameters.description:
- Less_than_1km
- Less_than_3km
- Less_than_5km
You can select more than one, separated by commas.

optional_parameters.name: room_facilities
optional_parameters.description:
Following: Private_pool<->Ocean_view<->Kitchen_Kitchenette<->Washing_machine<->Kitchen<->Air_conditioning<->Balcony<->Private_bathroom<->Refrigerator<->Childrens_cribs<->Terrace<->Bathtub<->Linens<->View<->TV<->Lake_view<->Kitchenware<->Mountain_view<->Hot_tub<->Pool_with_a_view<->Dining_table
Ex:Private_pool,Ocean_view

optional_parameters.name: facilities
optional_parameters.description:
Following: Parking<->Free_WiFi<->Restaurant<->Pet_friendly<->Room_service<->24_hour_front_desk<->Fitness_center<->Non_smoking_rooms<->Airport_shuttlev<->Facilities_for_disabled_guests<->Family_rooms<->Spa<->Electric_vehicle_charging_station<->Swimming_pool
Ex:Parking,Free_WiFi,Restaurant

optional_parameters.name: property_type
optional_parameters.description:
Following: VacationHomes<->EntireHomesandApartments<->Hotels<->Villas<->Apartments<->Resorts<->Campgrounds<->LuxuryTents<->BedandBreakfasts<->ResortVillages<->Guesthouses<->Lodges<->Homestays<->CountryHouses
Ex:VacationHomes,EntireHomesandApartments

optional_parameters.name: room_accessibility
optional_parameters.description:
Entire_unit_located_on_ground_floor<->Upper_floors_accessible_by_elevator<->Entire_unit_wheelchair_accessible<->Toilet_with_grab_rails<->Adapted_bath<->Roll_in_shower<->Walk_in_shower<->Raised_toilet<->Lower_sink<->Emergency_cord_in_bathroom<->Shower_chair
You can select more than one, separated by commas.

optional_parameters.name: property_rating
optional_parameters.description: List rating 0 - 5. Ex: 0,1,2

optional_parameters.name: min_bathroom
optional_parameters.description: Max:4

optional_parameters.name: sustainable_level
optional_parameters.description: Max:4

optional_parameters.name: bed_preference
optional_parameters.description:
Twin beds: 2
Double bed: 5

optional_parameters.name: review_score
optional_parameters.description: List of review score 60,70,80,90

optional_parameters.name: childrenAges
optional_parameters.description: List of ages of children, children under 2 limit of 1. Ex: 6,7,1

optional_parameters.name: selected_currency
optional_parameters.description: The value of Currency->code field returned in Example Responses of /Langue-Currency.

optional_parameters.name: lang
optional_parameters.description: The value of Language->code field returned in Example Responses of /Langue-Currency.

optional_parameters.name: cancellation_policy
optional_parameters.description:
- Free_cancellation
- No_prepayment
You can select more than one, separated by commas.

optional_parameters.name: sort
optional_parameters.description:
- Homes &Apartments first: upsort_bh
- Price (lowest first): price
- Best reviewed & Lowest price: review_score_and_price
- Rating (high to low): class
- Rating (low to high): class_asc
- Rating & price: class_and_price
- Top review: bayesian_review_score
- Distance form dowstown: distance_from_search

api_list.name: /Langue-Currency
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://booking-com16.p.rapidapi.com/home"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "booking-com16.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://booking-com16.p.rapidapi.com/home"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "booking-com16.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: /list/flight/Return

required_parameters.name: country
required_parameters.description: The value of Language->countryFlag field returned in Example Responses of /Langue-Currency.

required_parameters.name: location_from
required_parameters.description: The value of cityCode field returned in …/auto_complete/flight.

required_parameters.name: location_to
required_parameters.description: The value of cityCode field returned in …/auto_complete/flight.

optional_parameters.name: price
optional_parameters.description:
min,max Ex:1000,10000
The minimum and maximum limit values are displayed in resultSetMetaData->priceRange field returned in …/list/flight/One-way.

optional_parameters.name: trip_return_arrival_time
optional_parameters.description:
Ex:0,48600000
Miliseconds: Time in a day (rounded up to 30 minutes) * 3600000.
Ex: 13h30 is 13.5 * 3600000 = 48600000

optional_parameters.name: trip_return_departure_time
optional_parameters.description:
Ex:0,48600000
Miliseconds: Time in a day (rounded up to 30 minutes) * 3600000.
Ex: 13h30 is 13.5 * 3600000 = 48600000

optional_parameters.name: trip_arrival_time
optional_parameters.description:
Ex:0,48600000
Miliseconds: Time in a day (rounded up to 30 minutes) * 3600000.
Ex: 13h30 is 13.5 * 3600000 = 48600000

optional_parameters.name: airlines
optional_parameters.description:
The airlines code in …/list/flight/One-way …->resultSetMetaData->marketingCarriers
Ex:OG,UK

optional_parameters.name: travel_time
optional_parameters.description:
Miliseconds: The maximum limit is 62 hours (rounded up to 0.5) * 3600000.
Ex: 25.5h is 91800000

optional_parameters.name: max_stops
optional_parameters.description: 0 or 1 default to All

optional_parameters.name: trip_departure_time
optional_parameters.description:
Ex:0,48600000
Miliseconds: Time in a day (rounded up to 30 minutes) * 3600000.
Ex: 13h30 is 13.5 * 3600000 = 48600000

optional_parameters.name: list_childAge
optional_parameters.description: List of ages of children, children under 2 limit of 1. Ex: 6,7,1

optional_parameters.name: cabinClass
optional_parameters.description:
- ECONOMY
- PREMIUM_ECONOMY
- BUSINESS
- FIRST

optional_parameters.name: direct
optional_parameters.description: Show only direct flights? Default: false
